Odaily Planet Daily News According to official news, Megabit will be officially upgraded to MGBX at 00:00 (SGT) on April 12, 2025, and the platform domain name will be changed to mgbx.com. This brand upgrade covers several important modules such as product interface, access domain name and international services. The highlights of this upgrade are as follows: 
-App product interface is completely redesigned: The mobile App interface has been fully optimized, and users will enjoy a clearer visual style, smoother operation experience and more reasonable function layout. After the update, users can experience the new interface style at the first time; 
-Platform domain name upgrade: In order to support the brand's internationalization strategy, MGBX will enable a new domain name: mgbx.com, and provide global users with a more stable access experience; 
-International version is officially launched: MGBX international version will be fully released, supporting multi-language interface, helping global users to easily access the platform, providing a more stable user experience and localization support; 
*Contract experience gold function is launched: MGBX will provide users with special trading funds to help them explore contract trading strategies with zero risk and obtain real benefits in trading.
